<% content_for :title, "About Us | Jack SaaS" %>

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">About Jack SaaS</h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600">We're a dedicated team of developers helping businesses automate workflows and build custom software solutions that drive real results.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="aspect-square rounded-2xl bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="text-center p-8">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 md:w-40 md:h-40 rounded-full bg-blue-200 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-blue-700">J</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-blue-700 font-medium text-lg">Jack Nielsen</p>
            <p class="text-blue-600">Founder & Lead Developer</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -z-10 -bottom-4 -right-4 w-full h-full rounded-2xl bg-blue-200"></div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 text-sm font-medium mb-4">Our Story</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">From Frustration to Creation</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-slate-600 text-lg">
          <p>Jack SaaS was born from a simple observation: too many businesses were drowning in manual processes that could be easily automated with the right software.</p>
          <p>After working with dozens of companies as a freelance developer, I saw the same patterns repeat—teams spending hours on data entry, struggling with disconnected tools, and missing opportunities to scale.</p>
          <p>In 2020, I founded Jack SaaS with a mission: to help businesses work smarter, not harder. Since then, we've helped 50+ companies automate their workflows.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">To empower businesses with custom software solutions that automate workflows, reduce manual work, and enable sustainable growth.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8">
      <% [
        { title: "Innovation", desc: "We stay ahead of technology trends to deliver modern, scalable solutions.", icon: "💡" },
        { title: "Partnership", desc: "We view every project as a partnership. Your success is our success.", icon: "❤️" },
        { title: "Quality", desc: "We never compromise on code quality, security, or user experience.", icon: "🛡️" },
        { title: "Transparency", desc: "Clear communication, honest timelines, and no hidden surprises.", icon: "👥" }
      ].each do |value| %>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-2xl">
            <%= value[:icon] %>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2"><%= value[:title] %></h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600"><%= value[:desc] %></p>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-blue-600">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ready to Work Together?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-blue-100 mb-8">Let's discuss how we can help transform your business with custom software.</p>
      <a href="/quote" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-white text-blue-600 font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors">
        Get a Free Quote
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
